      "bullets": [
        "NSO Group's mercenary spyware targeted EU PEGA committee members, demonstrating the threat actor's willingness to breach its own investigators.",
        "Pegasus deployments leverage sophisticated zero-click exploits, bypassing standard mobile operating system security controls on iOS and Android.",
        "Organizations must prioritize rapid mobile patch management, threat hunting via MVT, and lockdown modes for high-value targets."
      ]
    },
