        "Use GitOps tools like ArgoCD and Renovate to automate homelab Kubernetes updates and application dependency patches without manual intervention.",
        "Replace complex self-hosted VPNs and ingress with zero-trust overlays like Tailscale and Cloudflare Tunnels to eliminate firewall and DNS maintenance.",
        "Implement auto-updating container runners like Watchtower or Keel alongside k3s to keep microservices secure and current passively."
      ]
